<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一小会，玛莎阿姨买完东西回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好奇怪啊！”她注意到了被弄脏的地垫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子们？你们在家吗？”她大声叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32532</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在这里！”厨房里传来了一个声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32533</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39276</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨一手提着东西，一手抱着兰姆走过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39277</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她走进厨房的时候，鲍比正在吃第二块花生酱三明治。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，天哪！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她喘着气扔掉了手里的袋子，差点把兰姆也扔了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是谁？”她朝着鲍比大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>65701</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>鲍比从他的三明治里抬起头来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>65702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是我，玛莎阿姨。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69843</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76012</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但玛莎阿姨当然认不出坐在她家厨房里的这个男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76013</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80034</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨赶紧把兰姆放下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>赛伊走了进来，他洗完澡后已经焕然一新。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，我现在也要个三明治。”他对他弟弟说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？还有一个？”玛莎阿姨大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98980</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她警惕地抓起了一个扫帚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玛莎阿姨！”赛伊试着解释。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111045</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不是你阿姨！”她大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111046</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么知道我名字的？”她朝着他们的脸挥舞着扫帚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122853</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>楼上潘瑟正盯着镜子里的那个美丽姑娘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122854</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“潘瑟，我应该穿我的粉色衬衫还是蓝色那件？”简在隔壁叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不知道。选你喜欢的吧。”潘瑟漫不经心地回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟越来越觉得自己一点都不好看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果我很美的话，我应该更快乐才对。”她一直都这么想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她将脸转到一边，还在看着镜子里的那个自己。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166254</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我变美了。”她说着，好像要说服自己一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166255</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>镜子里那个看着她的“自己”是谁呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简走进了房间里，打断了潘瑟的思考。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们下去吧。我听见玛莎阿姨的声音了。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183179</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟看着她的妹妹。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185641</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190112</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦！”她呼吸急促地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190113</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196181</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>简四处看了一下，说：“怎么了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196182</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟摇摇头：“没事，只不过……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”简问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210587</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没认出来你。”潘瑟尴尬地回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216006</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>厨房里，赛伊和鲍比遇上了麻烦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216007</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220787</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们会告诉你真相。”赛伊恳求说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220788</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224256</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是赛伊，那是鲍比。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224257</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228160</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨不是那么容易骗的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228161</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你觉得我傻吗？”她说，“你不是赛伊，你也不是鲍比！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235189</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这个时候，潘瑟和简走进了厨房。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245463</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“玛莎阿姨！你在干什么？”她们叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245464</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨愣住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>254444</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们还有多少人在这里？”她大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>254445</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛莎阿姨生气的声音让兰姆哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263524</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>潘瑟跑过去安慰她的小弟弟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263525</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268654</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没事儿的，兰姆。姐姐在这呢。”她说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268655</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274946</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想把兰姆抱起来，但兰姆却哭得更厉害了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么回事？是我啊！”潘瑟的声音都颤抖了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但兰姆睁大的眼睛好像在说他根本不认识她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你给我离那个孩子远点！”玛莎阿姨说着用她的扫帚猛拍潘瑟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>303858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“兰姆？”潘瑟依旧不放弃，“我是你姐姐啊。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>303859</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>兰姆再次大哭起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307082</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我受够了！”玛莎阿姨大叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315118</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“出去！你们都给我出去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她举起了扫帚，像棒球棒一样四下挥舞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320755</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325277</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴斯家的孩子们沮丧地跑出了房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325278</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>331801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不仅仅是玛莎阿姨，连小婴儿兰姆都不认识他们了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>331802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>340592</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不敢相信，兰姆不认识我了。”潘瑟大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>340593</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>346223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你应该高兴才对啊！”赛伊语气激烈地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>346224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>348801</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不是想变漂亮嘛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>348802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>353390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不怪兰姆！”鲍比喘着气说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>353391</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>362929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我都认不出你了。我也认不出我自己了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>